" It is very likely," said Bernard. " And if he has, 
you may be sure he writes them." 

"Order and method!" Mrs. Vivian exclaimed. 
" With his immense property those virtues are neces- 
sary." 

Bernard glanced at her a moment 

"My dear Lovelock," he said to himself, "you are 
