" My husband is very kind," she said gently. 

She had hardly spoken the words when Gordon 
came in. He stopped a moment on seeing Bernard, 
glanced at his wife, blushed, flushed, and with a loud, 
frank exclamation of pleasure, grasped his friend by 
both hands. It was so long since he had seen Ber- 
