" Yes, it 's very long," he said ; " it 's very pleasant. 
I have only just arrived ; I met Miss Vivian." 

" And you are not coming in ? " asked Angela's 
mother, very graciously. 

" Your daughter has not asked me ! " said Bernard. 

" Ah, my dearest," murmured Mrs. Vivian, looking 

at the girl 

Her daughter returned her glance, and then the 



