" We will go this evening." 

" I shall look for you eagerly," Bernard rejoined, 
" Auf wiedersehen, as we used to say at Baden ! " 

Mrs. Vivian waved him a response over the gate, 
her daughter gave him a glance from the threshold, 
and he took his way back to his inn. 



