speak to him. 

" When Blanche comes to see us, you must be sure 
to come with her," she said, with a friendly smile. 

Goi'don looked at her, but he said nothing. 

" We were so sorry to hear she is out of health," 
Angela went on. 

18 



274 *  

Still Gordon was silent, with his eyes fixed on her 
