some reason, at this moment, Bernard flushed. 

He rose quickly and walked away to the window 
where he stood looking out into the darkness. " The 
devil — the devil 1 " he murmured to himself ; " she 
does n't even know we are to be married — Gordon 
has n't been able to trust himself to tell her ! " And 
this fact seemed pregnant with evidence as to Gor- 
