Later she wrote that Blanche had in fact " backed 
out," and would not come to stay with them, having 
given as . an excuse that she was perpetually trjdng 
on dresses, and that at Mrs. Vivian's she should be at 



 331 

an inconvenient distance from the temple of these 
sacred rites, and the high priest who conducted the 
